<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="vi">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Tạm khóa đăng nhập - movieCC</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        body {
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            background: #0a0a0a;
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            color: #e0e0e0;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .bg-gradient {
            position: fixed;
            inset: 0;
            background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 30% 20%, rgba(244, 171, 180, 0.08) 0%, transparent 50%),
                        radial-gradient(ellipse at 70% 80%, rgba(244, 171, 180, 0.05) 0%, transparent 50%);
        }
        .container {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 440px;
            padding: 48px 36px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
            border-radius: 20px;
            backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
            box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
        }
        .lock-icon {
            width: 80px;
            height: 80px;
            margin: 0 auto 24px;
            background: rgba(244, 171, 180, 0.1);
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            animation: pulse 2s ease-in-out infinite;
        }
        .lock-icon svg { color: #F4ABB4; }
        @keyframes pulse {
            0%, 100% { box-shadow: 0 0 0 0 rgba(244, 171, 180, 0.2); }
            50% { box-shadow: 0 0 0 16px rgba(244, 171, 180, 0); }
        }
        h1 {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            color: #fff;
        }
        .desc {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: #888;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 28px;
        }
        .countdown-box {
            background: rgba(244, 171, 180, 0.08);
            border: 1px solid rgba(244, 171, 180, 0.15);
            border-radius: 14px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 28px;
        }
        .countdown-label {
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1.5px;
            color: #999;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        .countdown {
            font-size: 2.8rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: #F4ABB4;
            font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;
        }
        .progress-bar {
            width: 100%;
            height: 4px;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
            border-radius: 4px;
            margin-top: 16px;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .progress-fill {
            height: 100%;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #F4ABB4, #FED3DD);
            border-radius: 4px;
            transition: width 1s linear;
        }
        .btn-back {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
            padding: 12px 28px;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
            border-radius: 12px;
            color: #ccc;
            font-size: 0.88rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
        .btn-back:hover {
            background: rgba(244, 171, 180, 0.1);
            border-color: rgba(244, 171, 180, 0.3);
            color: #F4ABB4;
        }
        .tip {
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 0.78rem;
            color: #555;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="bg-gradient"></div>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="lock-icon">
            <svg width="36" height="36" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <rect x="3" y="11" width="18" height="11" rx="2" ry="2" />
                <path d="M7 11V7a5 5 0 0 1 10 0v4" />
                <circle cx="12" cy="16" r="1" />
            </svg>
        </div>
        <h1>Tạm khóa đăng nhập</h1>
        <p class="desc">Bạn đã nhập sai quá nhiều lần. Vui lòng đợi trước khi thử lại để bảo vệ tài khoản.</p>
        <div class="countdown-box">
            <div class="countdown-label">Thử lại sau</div>
            <div class="countdown" id="countdown"><%= minutes %>:<%= String(seconds).padStart(2, '0') %></div>
            <div class="progress-bar">
                <div class="progress-fill" id="progressFill"></div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <a href="/" class="btn-back">
            <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <path d="M19 12H5" /><polyline points="12 19 5 12 12 5" />
            </svg>
            Về trang chủ
        </a>
        <p class="tip">Giới hạn: 5 lần đăng nhập mỗi 5 phút</p>
    </div>
    <script nonce="<%= typeof nonce !== 'undefined' ? nonce : '' %>">
        let total = <%= retryAfter %>;
        const initialTotal = total;
        const el = document.getElementById('countdown');
        const bar = document.getElementById('progressFill');
        bar.style.width = '100%';
        const tick = setInterval(() => {
            total--;
            if (total <= 0) {
                clearInterval(tick);
                window.location.href = '/dang-nhap';
                return;
            }
            const m = Math.floor(total / 60);
            const s = total % 60;
            el.textContent = m + ':' + String(s).padStart(2, '0');
            bar.style.width = ((total / initialTotal) * 100) + '%';
        }, 1000);
    </script>
</body>
</html>
